      "content": "That's a good start. It captures the tone well. Can you expand on it a bit? Have Sterling describe what he actually sees when he looks at the tribes they've encountered—how they live, their lack of \"proper\" way of life, etc. I want him to explain to the crew why it's so necessary for them to step in and provide that structure because the locals seemingly can't do it themselves. Use that formal, condescending Victorian style.",
